Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到朋友了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我帮你包饺子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.30,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}午后的窗口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 怎么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.90,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得抓紧了 爸爸快回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是户高女士送来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要我传个话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出去的话会遭殃的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.70,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱还真是喜欢樱桃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么倒掉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快点做你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 安田太太 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱桃你吃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您的款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在问你味道怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 非常美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清除饺子的余味大概正好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家昨晚有些味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心点可不行啊 安田太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在用大蒜的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和乡下独门独户可不一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种程度上可以说是共同生活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 你们两个也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说到这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田太太才刚刚从乡下出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田太太 似乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您家的女儿被编到我家女儿那个班了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心点儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间如果也能和睦相处就好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田太太 得小心点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里要是得罪了户高太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后连你老公和女儿都会受牵连的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.00,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是独揽大权的分公司经理夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉不觉得有股臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是饺子的气味啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饺子 这不是很糟糕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超糟糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做过什么让高户家的由理亚不开心的事情了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们说我有饺子味 很看不起我 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快开门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 这么不顺心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 突然被分公司经理叫出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被大骂了一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是惹恼了他太太吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是什么话 明明是她不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你不会真的做了什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着啊 我什么都没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 不要引起纠纷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟那个分公司经理没有相处好就糟了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 朋友要来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他可是很厉害的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也好好期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 现在就上门来打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是装不在家的话 可饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 你在家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门啊 太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你把我叫来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.60,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 快让我进去 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快开门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被别人听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听到没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.80,0:09:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 请住手 求求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在不是悠闲漫步的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家好像出了什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有个年轻的男人闯了进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你妈妈有外遇了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了啊 亲人有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了啊 你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安田太太 可怜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 振作点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 住在这里要是惹恼了那个人就算了完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会这么倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是户高太太她自己不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户高太太？ 到底发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐啊 由理亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啊 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真不错啊 给我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生日还没到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么早就让自己老一岁嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真没礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.00,0:12:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们 是他们的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户高太太和我妈妈之间到底发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知真相后我要报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话 妈妈她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不要看到妈妈难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法帮助你的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的就只有复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.90,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你还要消除怨恨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就让你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是一切开始的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得相当不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想这些被散布出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事就别到处说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要是多嘴的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 接下来就轮到你女儿遭殃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真的假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.20,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 求求你了 快停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.00,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲真不走运\N无意中看到了不该看到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么不走运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对的明明是由理亚的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么一定要欺负我妈妈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 不过 所以我才会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我做了什么好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有立足之地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 公司里也都在流传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.50,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在外面勾引年轻男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.60,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是户高太太她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 根本连听都不听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.20,0:17:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直你只顾着自己的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是靠谁才过上现在这种日子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家已经一团糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.00,0:17:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是送来给您的东西 太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.90,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 误会啊误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被这个男人强迫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要撒谎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你勾引那个男人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我啊 我才是受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个恶心的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这个男人强迫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在学校被欺负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞外遇的原来是户高太太啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只发情的母狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子丢脸丢大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 虽然有点年纪了但身材不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都给我消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到悲欢哀乐的欲望尽头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不幸 但这里很适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我做的事情究竟是不是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 早上好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.10,0:22:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人受不了啊 你妈妈的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和男人私奔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当分公司经理太太也不容易啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了啊 小孩子是无罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.40,0:22:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也恢复了往日笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也能算是幸福的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.90,0:22:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能一生都这么幸福下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.50,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我结束一生的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会因为那天那时我所做的事得到报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当看到胸口的这个刻印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.90,0:22:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.00,0:23:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
