Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.40,0:24:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红 彩花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.70,0:24:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何如此怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.50,0:24:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人一点都不爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.60,0:24:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 还想将我的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.50,0:24:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为女演员的未来给毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.70,0:24:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那家伙流放到地狱
